      "options": {
        "content": "## 🔍 Comandos de arranque\n\n**Fase 0 — Core E4 (smf2 + upf2):**\n```bash\nmake core-5g-up\n# Luego make e4 lo levanta automáticamente\n```\n\n**Fase 1 — gNBs (secuencial):**\n```bash\n# 1. srsRAN (referencia N2)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-srs up -d srsgnb_zmq\n\n# 2. UERANSIM gNB1 (SD=000001)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-ueransim up -d nr_gnb\n\n# 3. UERANSIM gNB2 (SD=000001 + SD=000002)\ndocker compose -f ran.yaml --profile ran-5g-e4 up -d nr_gnb2\n# Verificar: amf_gnb_count == 3\n```\n\n**Fase 2 — UEs válidos:**\n```bash\ndocker compose ... up -d srsue_5g_zmq  # SD=000001\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue          # gNB1 SD=000001\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue2         # gNB2 SD=000001\ndocker compose ... up -d nr_ue3         # gNB2 SD=000002 → upf2\n# Verificar: amf_ue_count == 4\n# Verificar: nr_ue3 IP en 192.168.200.x\n```",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.3.0",
      "title": "🔍 Comandos arranque",
      "type": "text"
    },
